<BRANCH TIMEOUT="" SWITCH="/sFoundARec">
  <COMMENT> if we found the one and only record that we are looking for... </COMMENT>

  <!-- nodes -->

<SEQUENCE NAME="true" TIMEOUT="" EXIT-ON="FAILURE">
  <COMMENT> ...extract all the necessary fields from dbOutput into docAliasSettings and then exit the loop </COMMENT>

  <!-- nodes -->

<MAP TIMEOUT="" MODE="STANDALONE">
  <COMMENT> extract the basic fields first, including the concat of ENAPARTNER+ENAALIAS columns, as well as the keys needed for updating the accessed date </COMMENT>
